Custos — Non-Custodial Self-Hosted Execution Runner
Copyright 2026 The Alephain Guild

This product is part of The Alephain Guild ecosystem
(https://github.com/the-alephain-guild), a philosophy-driven, AI-augmented
quantitative research and trading platform.

Custos is the self-hosted execution host of the ecosystem: a daemon that
operators run on their own infrastructure, holding their own venue API keys
in a local vault. It is published as open source (Apache-2.0) from day one so
that operators can audit the code before entrusting it with their keys — the
verifiable fulfillment of the ecosystem's non-custodial red line.

